			</p>
			<p class='flex items-center gap-2 max-md:justify-center'>
				<Icon
					name='email'
					width={30}
					height={30}
					class='max-md:hidden'
					aria-hidden
				/>
				<span>belozupkociprianoadv@gmail.com</span>
			</p>
		</div>
		<address>
			R. Abdala Miguel Sarraf, 347<br />Centro, Rebou√ßas - PR, 84550-000
		</address>
	</div>
	<p class='py-1 text-xs'>Todos os direitos reservados | 2023</p>
</footer>
